data.description: Deal-2-Deal Custom home located in Haciendas Del Rio Subdivision. This home features 4 bedroom, 2 baths plus a Theater Room with an open floor plan that flows from kitchen to dining to living room. When it's a movie everyone wants to watch, no need to go out. You'll make good use of the theater room for family or friends on any occasion. Deal 2 Deal features gourmet kitchens in all their homes, to include pot filler with so much more.
